qualified teacher?</i>

907
01:01:29,991 --> 01:01:32,979
Well, now,
I'll tell you this, boy.

908
01:01:32,980 --> 01:01:36,480
If I know something
you don't know, then I'm
qualified to teach you.

909
01:01:36,490 --> 01:01:39,995
