ever taught before?

911
01:01:44,000 --> 01:01:46,999
Well, yes, you might say so.

912
01:01:47,000 --> 01:01:50,499
I recollect a time
there was about 50 men...

913
01:01:50,500 --> 01:01:56,000
I learned them all to shoot
and take care of their rifles.
I was the only teacher they had.

914
01:01:56,010 --> 01:01:59,509
But in school?
That was in the army.

915
01:01:59,510 --> 01:02:04,510
<i>In the civil war!
Right there's the first thing
I'm gonna learn ya!</i>

916
01:02:04,520 --> 01:02:08,025
The proper name is
"the war between the states,"
'cause that's what it was!

917
01:02:08,026 --> 01:02:10,519
<i>[ Johnny ]
You can look
in the history books.</i>

918
01:02:10,520 --> 01:02:13,519
They call it the civil war.
What about that?
Yeah!

919
01:02:13,520 --> 01:02:16,020
I don't need to look
in no books!

920
01:02:16,030 --> 01:02:18,529
I was there,
Shiloh to appomattox,

921
01:02:18,530 --> 01:02:23,029
