a ringtail rebel!

923
01:02:25,040 --> 01:02:28,550
Otherwise,
you wouldn't object to it
being called the civil war!

924
01:02:30,040 --> 01:02:32,539
I done my fighting
for the confederacy...

925
01:02:32,540 --> 01:02:35,040
