if that's what you mean.

926
01:02:35,050 --> 01:02:37,560
I thought so.
I knew it from the start.

927
01:02:38,050 --> 01:02:42,050
The important thing ain't
what you know from the start,
it's what you learn goin' along.

928
01:02:42,550 --> 01:02:46,050
We should have learned
one lesson from that war:

929
01:02:46,060 --> 01:02:48,070
About our country
staying united!

930
01:02:48,071 --> 01:02:54,060
<i>Abraham Lincoln said,
